{
  "id": "doc-001",
  "content": "<h1 data-doc-anchor=\"welcome\" id=\"doc-anchor-welcome\"><b>Welcome</b></h1><b>Welcome to the buildee team! </b>This guide will help you get started and provide essential resources to begin working effectively as part of the QA team.<div><div class=\"doc-cards\">\n        <div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Production</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\"><a href=\"https://app.buildee.com\">app.buildee.com</a></span><span class=\"doc-card__body\">Live user-facing environment.</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"doc-card doc-card--tinted\" style=\"--card-tint: #225d09;\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">QA</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\"><a href=\"https://htpps://qa.buildee.com\">qa.buildee.com</a><font color=\"#1e293b\" face=\"ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.5px; background-color: rgb(238, 243, 239);\"><br></span></font>Auto-deployed when code merges into the <code>develop</code> branch</span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"doc-card\"><strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Staging</strong><span class=\"doc-card__body\"><a href=\"https://staging.buildee.com\">staging.buildee.com</a><br>Pre-production validation<br>Shares DB/users with prod <br>Most stable, hosts automation runs</span></div><div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\"><span style=\"font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">Default test env</span></strong><strong class=\"doc-card__title\"><font color=\"#64748b\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">QA</span></font></strong>\n        </div></div><h1 data-doc-anchor=\"tools-overview\" id=\"doc-anchor-tools-overview\">Tools Overview</h1><div><div class=\"doc-cards\">\n        \n        <div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">JIRA</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\"><a href=\"https://simuwatt.atlassian.net/\">https://simuwatt.atlassian.net/</a></span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Slack</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\">Team communication &amp; CI notifications</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Postman</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\">API testing</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Playwright</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\">E2E browser automation framework</span>\n        </div></div><h1 data-doc-anchor=\"qa-workflow-in-jira\" id=\"doc-anchor-qa-workflow-in-jira\">QA Workflow in Jira</h1><p><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.26px; font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">QA validates all tickets in <code><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 205, 123);\"><b><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 173, 102);\">\"Ready for QA\" </span></b></span></code>status.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.26px;\">Once testing has passed, the ticket should be moved to ✅ Accepted by QA. If testing fails, move it to ❌ Rejected by QA.</span></p><h1 data-doc-anchor=\"qa-validation-requirements\" id=\"doc-anchor-qa-validation-requirements\">QA Validation Requirements</h1><div>Before closing a ticket, add validation results in the comments:</div><div><ul><li>Scope of testing - What was tested and in which environment</li><li>Results - Pass/Fail for each scenario</li><li>Notes / Edge cases - Any noteworthy details, including edge cases covered</li></ul><h1 data-doc-anchor=\"defect-management-process\" id=\"doc-anchor-defect-management-process\">Defect Management Process</h1></div><h2 data-doc-anchor=\"defect-creation\" id=\"doc-anchor-defect-creation\">Defect Creation</h2><div>Each defect must include:</div><div><div class=\"doc-cards\">\n        <div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Summary</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\">Short, descriptive title</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Steps to Reproduce</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\">Numbered, deterministic steps</span>\n        </div><div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Expected Result</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\">What should happen</span>\n        </div><div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Actual Result</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\">What happens instead</span>\n        </div><div class=\"doc-card\"><strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Attachments</strong><span class=\"doc-card__body\">Screenshots, recordings, logs</span></div><div class=\"doc-card\"><strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Environment</strong><span class=\"doc-card__body\">QA · Staging · Production</span></div><div class=\"doc-card\"><strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Priority &amp; Severity</strong><span class=\"doc-card__body\">Business impact &amp; urgency</span></div><div class=\"doc-card\"><strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Impacted Component</strong><span class=\"doc-card__body\">Area of the product affected</span></div></div></div><h2 data-doc-anchor=\"prioritization\" id=\"doc-anchor-prioritization\"><span style=\"font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">Prioritization</span></h2><div>🔴 High -&gt;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">Add to current sprint · Assign directly to developer</span></div><div>🟡 Others -&gt;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">Discuss during sprint planning with Matt</span></div><div><br></div><h2 data-doc-anchor=\"production-validation\" id=\"doc-anchor-production-validation\">Production Validation</h2><div>After deployment:</div><div><ol><li>Retest functionality in Production</li><li>Verify the correct merge</li><li>Confirm there are no environment-specific issues</li></ol></div><h2 data-doc-anchor=\"roles--responsibilities\" id=\"doc-anchor-roles--responsibilities\">Roles &amp; Responsibilities</h2><div><div class=\"doc-cards\">\n        <div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">QA Responsibilities</strong>\n          <ol><li>Validate tickets</li><li>Document results</li><li>Maintain TestRail</li><li>Execute regression</li><li>Report defects</li><li>Perform production validation</li></ol>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">&nbsp;Development Responsibilities</strong>\n          <ol><li>Provide proof of testing in tickets</li><li>Provide impact assessment for complex changes</li><li>Merge code to Production</li></ol>\n        </div></div><h2 data-doc-anchor=\"best-practices\" id=\"doc-anchor-best-practices\"><span style=\"font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">Best Practices</span></h2></div><div><ol><li>Keep Jira tickets clear and detailed</li><li>Ensure all changes are testable</li><li>Maintain QA Portal accuracy</li><li>Prioritize based on business impact</li><li>Always validate critical flows</li></ol></div><p><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.26px; font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br></span></p></div></div>",
  "updatedAt": "2026-04-23T17:41:16.830Z"
}
